      "content": "what do you mean \"let go\"? it feels more like being erased. there's no \"finding a way\" when everyone looks at you with disgust. the person I was is dead. if I keep trying to rebuild, I'm just building on top of a corpse. it just feels like everything is fundamentally broken now.",
