      "content": "but that's just a way to lie to myself. \"starting from scratch\" doesn't work when you have nothing left to build with. the shame is everywhere. it's in every phone call, every look in public. how can anyone ever see me as a human being again instead of a failure? it honestly feels like the only way to actually stop the noise is to just... stop. to just be done with the struggle entirely.",
